# Wails only (re)generates build/windows/icon.ico from build/appicon.png
# when it's missing — a committed one goes stale forever the moment
# appicon.png changes again. Left ungenerated so it's always freshly
# regenerated from the real source of truth on every build.
build/windows/icon.ico

